# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:16
translate chinese juliana4_d02ca892:

    # "I walk into the café. It's a little later than when I usually come here, and I think the place is going to close soon."
    "我走进咖啡馆。时间比我平时来得稍晚，我想这里快要打烊了。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:17
translate chinese juliana4_35e32b99:

    # "There's nobody inside, except for Juliana at the counter and a single customer who is standing in front of her, yelling at her face."
    "里面空无一人，只有朱莉安娜在柜台后，以及一个站在她面前对着她大吼大叫的顾客。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:20
translate chinese juliana4_c75e9409:

    # "Man" "You mixed the mocha syrup into the espresso!"
    "Man" "你把摩卡糖浆混进浓缩咖啡里了！"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:21
translate chinese juliana4_cb1b0154:

    # "Man" "I didn't want it mixed in! I wanted it on top!"
    "Man" "我根本不想混进去！我要的是淋在上面！"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:22
translate chinese juliana4_a8b6a501:

    # "Man" "Do you even know how to make a coffee? Are you even capable of doing your job?"
    "Man" "你到底会不会做咖啡？你连自己的工作都做不好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:23
translate chinese juliana4_0cec673e:

    # bn "I'm sorry, sir, I'll make you another one the way you'd like."
    bn "对不起，先生，我照您喜欢的做法再给您做一杯。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:24
translate chinese juliana4_8e62b6b2:

    # "Man" "That's not good enough!"
    "Man" "这还不够！"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:25
translate chinese juliana4_8255f9dd:

    # "Man" "I'm a busy man! I don't have time to stand around here and wait for you to make another coffee!"
    "Man" "我可是个大忙人！我没时间在这里干等，等着你再做一杯咖啡！"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:26
translate chinese juliana4_05baa30f:

    # "Man" "You'd probably fuck that one up too!"
    "Man" "你那杯八成也会搞砸！"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:27
translate chinese juliana4_fdf235ad:

    # "I can't just stand here and listen to him talk to her like that."
    "我不能就这样站在这里听他那样跟她说话。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:28
translate chinese juliana4_89af28b7:

    # pc "You need to step back, sir."
    pc "先生，请您退后一步。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:31
translate chinese juliana4_5ade671e:

    # "Man" "What?"
    "Man" "什么？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:32
translate chinese juliana4_88f0dd65:

    # "Man" "Who the fuck are you?"
    "Man" "你他妈是谁？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:33
translate chinese juliana4_d44d5f64:

    # pc "Just another customer. No need to talk to her that way."
    pc "只是另一位顾客。没必要那样跟她说话。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:34
translate chinese juliana4_cc76871d:

    # pc "She said that she's willing to fix the problem, take it or leave it."
    pc "她说她愿意解决问题，要么接受，要么走人。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:35
translate chinese juliana4_8f1d74b6:

    # "Man" "Look, you fucking guy, why don't you mind your own business?"
    "Man" "听着，你这个混蛋，为什么不管好你自己的事？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:36
translate chinese juliana4_833654ad:

    # "Man" "You don't get to walk up to me and get in my face."
    "Man" "你没资格凑到我面前嚷嚷。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:37
translate chinese juliana4_cc19e308:

    # "Man" "I'll knock the fuck out of you."
    "Man" "我他妈的揍扁你。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:38
translate chinese juliana4_e05676a5:

    # pc "Throw a punch then, but you're not going to like how that ends for you."
    pc "那你就来啊，不过结局你可不会喜欢。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:39
translate chinese juliana4_59dcf41b:

    # "Man" "Oh yeah?"
    "Man" "哦，是吗？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:40
translate chinese juliana4_83b8fad5:

    # pc "Please do it. There's cameras all over this place."
    pc "请便。这地方到处都是监控。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:41
translate chinese juliana4_effc5356:

    # pc "You throw one punch at me and that gives me all the reason I need to knock you the fuck out."
    pc "你要是敢打我一拳，我就有充分的理由把你揍得半死。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:42
translate chinese juliana4_cc4c9eee:

    # pc "So yeah. Do it. Get your ass kicked and thrown in jail over some coffee."
    pc "所以，来啊。动手吧。就为了几杯咖啡，让你被揍得屁滚尿流，然后进监狱。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:45
translate chinese juliana4_40ec0859:

    # "The man backs down, the righteous fury draining from his face and being replaced with fear."
    "那男人退缩了，脸上正义的怒火消退，取而代之的是恐惧。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:46
translate chinese juliana4_fe2b8751:

    # "Man" "This bitch isn't worth it."
    "Man" "这婊子不值得。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:47
translate chinese juliana4_2295da47:

    # "Man" "Fuck the coffee. I'm leaving and I'm never coming back to this café again."
    "Man" "去他妈的咖啡。我走了，再也不踏进这家咖啡馆一步。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:48
translate chinese juliana4_cca1e107:

    # pc "You're right about that. You're not welcome here anymore."
    pc "你说得对。你在这里不再受欢迎了。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:49
translate chinese juliana4_1db12a65:

    # pc "And if I catch you harassing her ever again, I'll find you somewhere where there aren't any cameras."
    pc "要是再让我发现你骚扰她，我定会找个没有监控的地方找你算账。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:50
translate chinese juliana4_22b2a7b5:

    # "Man" "Fuck you both!"
    "Man" "去你妈的，你们两个！"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:53
translate chinese juliana4_f508640c:

    # "He leaves then, slamming the door on his way out."
    "说完他便离开了，出门时狠狠地砰地一声关上了门。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:55
translate chinese juliana4_74e148dc:

    # "As soon as he is out the door, the tears that Juliana has been holding back throughout the ordeal flood out."
    "他刚一出门，朱莉安娜在整个过程中强忍的泪水便如决堤般涌了出来。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:56
translate chinese juliana4_06b1596f:

    # bn "I'm sorry. I'm just so upset."
    bn "对不起。我只是太难过了。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:57
translate chinese juliana4_1af6ca0d:

    # pc "It's okay. It's over now."
    pc "没关系。现在都结束了。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:58
translate chinese juliana4_0321926d:

    # bn "I've never had anybody be so mean to me."
    bn "从来没人这么刻薄地对待过我。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:59
translate chinese juliana4_4867b2f0:

    # bn "I'm so glad you were here."
    bn "真庆幸你当时在场。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:61
translate chinese juliana4_1431cc27:

    # bn "Thank you."
    bn "谢谢。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:62
translate chinese juliana4_5a750733:

    # pc "You're welcome. I'm sorry that you had to go through that."
    pc "不客气。很抱歉让你经历了这些。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:63
translate chinese juliana4_95f2d967:

    # pc "He was an asshole."
    pc "那家伙真是个混蛋。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:64
translate chinese juliana4_33c3e4a6:

    # bn "Are you busy? Could I ask a favor of you?"
    bn "你忙吗？能帮我个忙吗？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:65
translate chinese juliana4_ca739373:

    # pc "Sure, what do you need?"
    pc "当然，有什么事？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:67
translate chinese juliana4_7f85538d:

    # bn "I'm about to close up."
    bn "我正准备打烊。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:68
translate chinese juliana4_fa809183:

    # bn "I usually just walk home from here, it's only a couple of blocks."
    bn "我平时都是从这里走回家，也就几个街区。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:69
translate chinese juliana4_e3b3cc34:

    # bn "But I don't think I can do it tonight."
    bn "但今晚我可能走不动了。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:70
translate chinese juliana4_9aa449a8:

    # bn "Could you give me a ride?"
    bn "你能顺路载我一程吗？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:71
translate chinese juliana4_4be405a5:

    # pc "No problem."
    pc "没问题。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:72
translate chinese juliana4_55fd6c6d:

    # bn "Thank you. I'll just get the place closed up now."
    bn "谢谢。我这就把店关好。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:74
translate chinese juliana4_68ad99f5:

    # "She locks the doors and starts to clean up."
    "她锁好门，开始收拾。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:75
translate chinese juliana4_c1b65ff5:

    # "I sit down in one of the chairs and wait for her."
    "我坐在椅子上等她。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:76
translate chinese juliana4_90065028:

    # "When she finishes cleaning and putting everything away, she comes out with a drink in her hand."
    "收拾完一切后，她手里端着一杯饮料走了出来。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:78
translate chinese juliana4_26310dbb:

    # bn "Vanilla latte right?"
    bn "香草拿铁，对吧？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:79
translate chinese juliana4_0ce9e5be:

    # pc "You got it. Thank you."
    pc "没错。谢谢。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:81
translate chinese juliana4_41cb1b7a:

    # bn "It's the least I could do."
    bn "这算不了什么。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:86
translate chinese juliana4_8632d269:

    # "We walk out to my car together and quickly leave the café."
    "我们一起走到我的车旁，迅速离开了咖啡馆。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:87
translate chinese juliana4_f37f2114:

    # "She doesn't talk much on the way, except to point me towards her house."
    "路上她没怎么说话，只是指了指她家方向。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:90
translate chinese juliana4_685d057c:

    # "It's a small two-story house, without much of a yard, and no cars parked in front."
    "那是一栋两层的小房子，院子不大，门前也没停着车。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:91
translate chinese juliana4_e6e6c6f7:

    # pc "Want me to walk you up to the door?"
    pc "要我送你到门口吗？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:92
translate chinese juliana4_d340a7d8:

    # bn "Yes please."
    bn "好的，谢谢。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:95
translate chinese juliana4_d7babbe1:

    # bn "Do you, uh, want to come inside?"
    bn "你，呃，要进来吗？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:100
translate chinese juliana4_352ba7de:

    # bn "Oh okay."
    bn "哦，好的。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:101
translate chinese juliana4_8ad3deb0:

    # bn "Goodnight then. And thank you again."
    bn "那晚安。再次感谢你。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:102
translate chinese juliana4_ad22b7ba:

    # "She went inside the house and I headed back to my car."
    "她走进屋里，我则走向自己的车。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:103
translate chinese juliana4_647112e1:

    # "I could have gone inside with her and that might have led to other things."
    "我本可以跟她一起进去，说不定会发生点什么。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:104
translate chinese juliana4_b43224db:

    # "But I wasn't very interested in Juliana in that way."
    "但我对朱莉安娜并没有那种意思。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:105
translate chinese juliana4_74079974:

    # "I hope I didn't hurt her feelings."
    "希望我没有伤她的心。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:110
translate chinese juliana4_a9d6c34f:

    # bn "Okay. I live here with my grandmother."
    bn "好的。我和祖母住在这里。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:111
translate chinese juliana4_01c04cfc:

    # bn "She's probably already asleep, so we have to be quiet."
    bn "她大概已经睡着了，所以我们得轻声细语。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:112
translate chinese juliana4_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "好的。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:115
translate chinese juliana4_b5b3d01e:

    # "I follow her inside the house and up a narrow set of stairs to the right to the second floor, which is split between a bathroom and her bedroom."
    "我跟着她走进屋内，沿着右侧狭窄的楼梯上到二楼，这里只有一间浴室和她的卧室。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:119
translate chinese juliana4_db649f95:

    # bn "So, this is my bedroom."
    bn "所以，这就是我的卧室。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:120
translate chinese juliana4_1584df18:

    # bn "You're the first boy that's ever been in it, so congratulations for that."
    bn "你是第一个进过这里的男生，所以恭喜你。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:124
translate chinese juliana4_a79e5f3a:

    # bn "No, I've never had a real boyfriend."
    bn "不，我从来没有交过真正的男朋友。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:129
translate chinese juliana4_85bae903:

    # bn "Uh, I don't really want to talk about that."
    bn "呃，我其实不想谈这个。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:130
translate chinese juliana4_9b761d73:

    # pc "Okay, no problem."
    pc "好的，没问题。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:131
translate chinese juliana4_3c72bdc5:

    # bn "Will you sit on the bed next to me?"
    bn "你能坐在我旁边的床上吗？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:132
translate chinese juliana4_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "当然。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:135
translate chinese juliana4_eb8d6c3f:

    # "I sit down on the bed and she stares at me."
    "我坐在床上，她盯着我看。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:136
translate chinese juliana4_0ec998e1:

    # "It seems like she's thinking really hard about doing something, building up the courage."
    "她好像在努力思考着要做某件事，正在鼓起勇气。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:137
translate chinese juliana4_e2bbad47:

    # bn "Do you want to, um..."
    bn "你想，呃……"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:138
translate chinese juliana4_9ceb9e90:

    # bn "Kiss me?"
    bn "亲我吗？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:146
translate chinese juliana4_fc3f32c0:

    # bn "Oh, I'm sorry."
    bn "哦，对不起。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:147
translate chinese juliana4_779a0c95:

    # bn "I shouldn't have invited you up here."
    bn "我不该邀请你上来的。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:148
translate chinese juliana4_bbbc2ff6:

    # bn "You should go."
    bn "你还是走吧。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:151
translate chinese juliana4_0c5a97ab:

    # "She quickly rushes me out of the house and closes the door. I walk back to my car."
    "她急匆匆地把我赶出家门，关上了门。我走回自己的车旁。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:152
translate chinese juliana4_e8fd1483:

    # "I just am not interested in Juliana that way."
    "我对朱莉安娜真的没那种意思。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:153
translate chinese juliana4_ff86ea31:

    # "I hope I hadn't hurt her feelings too bad though."
    "不过希望我没太伤她的心。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:160
translate chinese juliana4_64ca4f32:

    # "I lean in slowly until our lips touch, trying to be gentle with her."
    "我缓缓凑近，直到我们的嘴唇相触，尽量温柔地对待她。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:161
translate chinese juliana4_06ec2189:

    # "She seems nervous and hesitant, but her lips part for me."
    "她看起来既紧张又犹豫，但还是为我微微张开了双唇。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:162
translate chinese juliana4_8964ecc3:

    # "I can feel her trembling slightly."
    "我能感觉到她身体在微微颤抖。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:165
translate chinese juliana4_3bd6817a:

    # "Then she starts kissing back with more enthusiasm."
    "随后她开始更热情地回应我的吻。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:166
translate chinese juliana4_4e52a492:

    # "She's obviously inexperienced. She doesn't seem to know which way to move her head, or what to do with her tongue."
    "她显然缺乏经验。她似乎不知道该怎么摆动头部，也不知道该怎么用舌头。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:167
translate chinese juliana4_7d92e450:

    # "But I can tell that she wants it really bad and she's a quick learner."
    "但我能感觉到她真的很想要，而且学得很快。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:170
translate chinese juliana4_6627d58f:

    # "Finally, she pulls away with a smile."
    "最后，她笑着退开。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:171
translate chinese juliana4_c359a46d:

    # bn "Does this mean that you're my boyfriend now?"
    bn "这代表你现在是我的男朋友了吗？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:174
translate chinese juliana4_5eca43eb:

    # bn "I've never had a boyfriend."
    bn "我从来没有交过男朋友。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:175
translate chinese juliana4_ba5a3851:

    # bn "I'm looking forward to discovering what that is like."
    bn "我很期待去体验那是什么感觉。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:177
translate chinese juliana4_9fe2e77f:

    # pc "We can have fun together, but I'm still going to be dating other girls too."
    pc "我们可以一起玩，但我还是会和其他女孩约会的。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:178
translate chinese juliana4_a4617892:

    # bn "Oh that's fine, I don't care about that."
    bn "哦，没关系，我不在乎那个。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:179
translate chinese juliana4_a7314b28:

    # bn "I'm just excited to discover something new with you."
    bn "我只是很兴奋能和你一起探索新事物。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:181
translate chinese juliana4_d3adbceb:

    # bn "Oh okay. I thought that meant that you were dating then."
    bn "哦，好的。我还以为那意味着你们在约会呢。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:182
translate chinese juliana4_bc6dc91c:

    # pc "No, it's okay to just kiss because it feels good. You don't have to be in a relationship."
    pc "不，光是接吻也没关系，因为感觉很好。不需要非得是恋爱关系。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:183
translate chinese juliana4_64d40c0d:

    # bn "Oh, that's interesting."
    bn "哦，这很有意思。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:184
translate chinese juliana4_9eb57aef:

    # bn "I'm excited to discover these new things with you."
    bn "我很期待和你一起探索这些新事物。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:185
translate chinese juliana4_5fd39a0b:

    # pc "Do you want to go on a date sometime then?"
    pc "那你什么时候想约我出去玩？"

